{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491270/extras/10.gif?t=1732517852\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Origin</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a plane plunged into the heart of Samomor town, 19 children started disappearing mysteriously. To break the cycle of sorrow, two brave students, you and Jack, embarked on a quest to uncover the root cause.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491270/extras/01-die.gif?t=1732517852\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Anyone can be eliminated. The story changes as each person disappears</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The life of each person is entirely in your hands. However, you will also bear all the consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491270/extras/Overview_Gif.gif?t=1732517852\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Real-time combat system that requires skill</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will die, a lot. But you won't die alone because you can befriend NPCs to die with you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491270/extras/02-Abilitygif.gif?t=1732517852\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Your abilities change based on your weapon</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each ability operates differently depending on the weapon you use.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491270/extras/03-Mix.gif?t=1732517852\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Craft your own abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can mix different abilities to create many random variations. With over 40 abilities and weapon skills from the skill tree, master the battles with your own crafted formula.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Other features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A complex story with many choices that can change the game's narrative completely</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Befriend and accompany humorous and edgy NPCs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fully open map with many caves to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Puzzles, mini-games, treasures, and special challenges scattered throughout</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your character's appearance with 40+ pieces of equipment</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First weapon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2491270/b2ea92528007506be5ac17c492f9adf1c23ff738.jpg"},{"name":"First Choice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2491270/8688e7f29b63c98ed1cccc32aa9c7b5ec9b6ee3e.jpg"},{"name":"Family Picture","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2491270/9c2a771005143b26cdc741af82b38d57784ef293.jpg"},{"name":"The Parasite","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2491270/339973c4dc179b9d126906880698f5a9dabef095.jpg"},{"name":"Mini Henry","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2491270/91abe45fc5693ff51ca1e429fad60f019ae2d4ac.jpg"},{"name":"Got Shot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2491270/67f37ee2411681b53a0cc2712bcadb1c62da3dfa.jpg"}],"total":6},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491270/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732517852","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491270/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732517852","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491270/1b307059aa81a0